00:02:09.270 --> 00:02:12.810
So when I'm doing a chest
press, 540 pounds here,

00:02:12.810 --> 00:02:16.140
300 pounds here, and
a hundred pounds here.

00:02:16.140 --> 00:02:19.800
So a very steep, variant curve.

00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:24.800
