00:02:29.870 --> 00:02:34.870
than I do here and incredibly
so more than when I'm here.

00:02:35.460 --> 00:02:37.763
So when I go through that experience,

00:02:39.080 --> 00:02:41.290
I'm fatiguing the muscle, in accordance

00:02:41.290 --> 00:02:42.950
with what the capacity is.

00:02:42.950 --> 00:02:45.990
I'm also keeping constant tension.

00:02:45.990 --> 00:02:48.610
So never letting slack come in the band.

00:02:48.610 --> 00:02:50.557
In fact, when somebody ever says,

00:02:50.557 --> 00:02:55.557
