00:03:00.340 --> 00:03:03.640
off and you're using
the device incorrectly.

00:03:03.640 --> 00:03:06.140
So you gotta keep constant tension.

00:03:06.140 --> 00:03:08.510
Now, body builders have
been using constant tension

00:03:08.510 --> 00:03:12.290
for a long time, just to make sure

00:03:12.290 --> 00:03:14.910
