00:03:17.480 --> 00:03:21.740
but we also apply that
constant tension principle.

00:03:21.740 --> 00:03:23.290
So you never let off.

00:03:23.290 --> 00:03:25.950
Now, from a central
nervous system standpoint,

00:03:25.950 --> 00:03:29.760
when people lift and they lock
